<item>
            <title>[VFS-51] [TMP] Root dir for temp filesystem should be temp system dir by default</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/VFS-51</link>
                <project id="12310495" key="VFS">Commons VFS</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Root dir for temp filesystem should be temp system dir by default, not root dir of system drive.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m using tmp filesystem to perform JUnit tests, and i need to clean up my root folder of C: every time after tests.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;1.0-RC8-SNAPSHOT, Windows XP, Sun JVM (1.4, 1.5, 1.6)&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12344645">VFS-51</key>
